Refactoring:

Instead of array, store the representation (DenseMatrix, TDenseMatrix)
inside the class. So it makes possible to implement in-place transpose, etc...
Make matrix representations private.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Functionality:

LU decomposition
general matrix inverse
back substitution
least squares solution

sparse vectors/matrices

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Performance:

vector performance improvements
  constant vector
  standard unit vector

matrix performance improvements
  diagonal matrices, identity matrix
  lower/upper triangular matrices
